data.description: Enjoy fresh air & your own little bit of heaven in this peaceful, gated neighborhood with great neighbors!  Home has extensive trim, arched entry ceiling, built-ins & surround sound; Open & spacious formal dining room & family room.  Large gourmet island kitchen has tons of countertop & storage space and opens to family room; family room has beuatiful tray ceiling, stone fireplace & lots of windows for natural light; tray ceiling, enormous closet & built-ins in primary bedroom; primary bath has separate tub, shower & double sinks; 3 large secondary  bedrooms are also downstairs.  Huge game/media room up with built-in entertainment center & full bath; could  be a 5th bedroom. Texas basement with A/C also up. Covered rear patio w/speakers.  Screened breezeway, great utility room & fenced backyard has lots of pool space. New roof in 2022. Sitting on an acre in a small quiet community in Magnolia ISD; this home has it ALL & is perfect for entertaining family& friends. LOW TAXES! HURRY!
